content: Haidee endears here's a couple of figure
sets that a friend gave me a childhood friend of mine named Doug Sanders and he
had these original Advanced Dungeons & Dragons action figure sets and I was
just like wow I had these when I was a kid younger but wow I mean we were just
kids when we had these and he still had him and gave him to me so I was just so
appreciative now when I open the boxes they're not exactly all the miniatures
from these two sets they're from various different sets there's a dragon the
large dragon from the dragon box there's some retainers and there's from
different sets so they're not necessarily from both these sets but
yeah look at that remember that insert foam there in the boxes that you can
keep your miniatures on nice and safe so let's take a closer look at these and
look at them now he did paint them to a pretty high standard for being a kid and
not all of them are painted but most of them are painted so I'm going to show
them to you and take a walk down memory lane and check out these up miniatures
